  "title": "Creative Content Producer | INX-B01",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Create eye-catching visuals, videos, and multimedia content for digital platforms</li><li>Collaborate with marketing teams to develop content aligned with campaign goals</li><li>Assist in managing content calendars and publishing schedules</li><li>Optimize content for SEO and audience engagement</li><li>Stay updated on content trends, design tools, and platform features</li><li>Support photo and video shoots, including basic editing and post-production</li><li>Help maintain brand consistency across all creative outputs</li><li>Contribute fresh ideas during brainstorming sessions and creative meetings</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li><li>Diploma and above</li><li>Training will be provided</li></li><li>Basic experience with design/video tools (e.g., Canva, Adobe Suite, CapCut)</li><li>Creative, detail-oriented, and visually inclined</li><li>Able to work collaboratively and accept constructive feedback</li></ul><p><strong>EA License Number: 25C2980</strong></p><p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong></p><p>By applying, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data for recruitment purposes in accordance with Singapore’s PDPA. Your application may be considered for this and other suitable roles.</p>",
